\
Semantic Topology runs a three-phase cycle inside every tick: **Update \uc0\u8594  Decide \u8594  Emit**.  \
This keeps the spatial shape of meaning aligned with latent embeddings, schema health, and ecological feedback.\
\
---\
\
### 1) Update\
- **Ingest**:  \
  - Embedding deltas (latent drift from Core/Bloom).  \
  - Global drift vector (Schema).  \
  - Bloom & Residue stats (reblooms, soot/ash transitions).  \
  - Tracer alerts (Spider tension, Beetle decay, Bee pollination, Whale macro-trends).  \
- **Recompute**:  \
  - Local coherence `C_i` for all nodes.  \
  - Edge tensions `\uc0\u964 _ij` and volatility scores.  \
  - Pigment field gradients (`\uc0\u8711 P`).  \
  - Residue pressure fields `\uc0\u961 _i`.  \
- **Soft Reproject**:  \
  - Nudge positions `x` toward latent embeddings (`e`) under motion budget.  \
  - Preserve edge continuity (no \'93tears\'94 for high-reliability edges).  \
\
---\
\
### 2) Decide\
- **Tension Response**  \
  - If `\uc0\u964 _ij` > threshold \u8594  schedule **Prune** (remove incoherent edge) or **Weave** (reinforce local manifold).  \
- **Cluster Morphology**  \
  - If cluster inertia + sustained co-fire high \uc0\u8594  **Fuse** clusters.  \
  - If entropy brittle + coherence low \uc0\u8594  **Fission** cluster.  \
- **Layer Moves**  \
