  - If surface lacks anchors but ash-rich nodes exist \uc0\u8594  **Lift** candidates (rebloom ascent).  \
- **Global Alignment**  \
  - If latent vs projected coherence drifts beyond tolerance \uc0\u8594  bounded **Reproject** across region.  \
- **Budget Enforcement**  \
  - Cap number of transforms per tick; overflow queued into next tick.  \
\
---\
