### 3) Emit\
- **Topology Delta**  \
  - Node movements (\uc0\u916 x, \u916 layer), edge updates (weights, prunes, weaves).  \
  - Cluster fusions/fissions with new IDs and provenance.  \
- **Sigil Stack**  \
  - Translate chosen operators into symbolic invocations for the Sigil Ring.  \
  - Example: `Purification.prune_edge`, `Weaving.reinforce_thread`, `Memory.lift_node`.  \
- **Snapshot Broadcast**  \
  - GUI: render node/edge shifts, pigment diffusion, tension overlays.  \
  - Schema: provide updated coherence/tension metrics for SHI recalculation.  \
  - Owl: log provenance (trigger, operator, guard conditions, invoker).  \
